results.description:
This is cardless credit you control. Bip is the brand-new cardless credit app with absolutely no hidden fees. 

Experience the simplicity of Bip and join a growing community of people wanting to go cardless. Check your eligibility today to be a part of it.

Here’s what you’ll get with Bip:

Quick and simple setup - Check your eligibility (there’s no impact on your credit score), then apply and add Bip to Apple Pay and you’re good to go. If you’ve already checked your eligibility online, simply pick up your application in app to continue. 

Tap. Cap. Control - Set yourself Spending Caps, get instant balance updates and copy your Bip details from within the app to spend online. With no card, there’s less hanging around.

No hidden fees - Just one interest rate. That’s it. No annual charges, no late payment or over limit fees and nothing extra for using Bip abroad.

24/7 support - In-app messaging means that you’ll always have support to help you with any questions you may have. Need help setting your Spending Caps? Want general advice about your cardless credit? We’re on standby.

Boosted Payments - See how much you could save yourself by paying more off each month. Use the in-app payment slider to compare boosted payments against your minimum.

Safe and secure payments -  Supported by Mastercard, Bip has the standard fraud prevention and purchase protections you’d get with a regular credit card. Apple Pay is both a safe and secure way of making contactless purchases, and just as easy as a plastic credit card.

Decide how credit works for you – managing your credit has never been easier.

Download today to get started! 

Representative 29.9% APR (variable). Starting credit limit from £250 to £1,200.
Don’t forget: Failure to make payments on time or to stay within your credit limit may make obtaining credit in the future more expensive and difficult.
Credit available only to UK residents aged 18 and over. Subject to status. Terms apply.
The APR and credit limit applicable to your account will depend on our assessment of your application.
Credit is provided by NewDay Ltd. NewDay Ltd and NewDay Cards Ltd are companies registered in England and Wales with registered numbers 7297722 and 4134880 respectively. They form part of the NewDay group of companies. The registered office for these companies is 7 Handyside Street, London, N1C 4DA. NewDay Ltd and NewDay Cards Ltd are authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) with numbers 690292 and 682417 respectively. NewDay Ltd is also authorised by the FCA under the Payment Services Regulation 2017 (ref no: 555318) for the provision of payment services. Bip is a trademark of NewDay Cards Ltd, which is used under license by NewDay Ltd.

results.description:
Over 4 million people now bank with Monzo to spend, save and sort their money.

BANKING MADE EASY

• Get better visibility and more control over all your money. Open a full UK bank account from your phone, for free.

• Or move everything to Monzo using the free Current Account Switch Service. It's fully guaranteed, takes one week and we can set it up in minutes.

PICK AN ACCOUNT THAT SUITS YOU

It's our mission to make money work for everyone, so we've created different accounts for different needs.

• Monzo Plus
The account that puts money in your hands. Full financial visibility, with your other bank accounts and credit cards all in one place. Get interest on your money, personalised budgeting, a holographic card and so much more.

• Monzo 
Our original, free account. With instant spending notifications, easy ways to send money, Pots for separating your savings and more.

• Monzo Joint Accounts
Bring your money together with our free joint account. Pool your resources with someone to make life easier to manage. See who's paying for what, set spending budgets and we'll send both of you a separate card.

• Monzo Business Lite
The best of Monzo but for your business, with no monthly fee. A full UK current account including mobile and web access, free instant UK bank transfers, budgeting, digital receipts, award-winning customer support and more.  

• Monzo Business Pro
Your business' finances taken care of, for £5 a month. A full UK current account including everything in Business Lite, plus Tax Pots, integrated accounting, multi-user access for limited companies, invoicing and more.

KEEP YOUR MONEY SAFE

• Just like any other bank, your eligible deposits up to £85,000 are protected by the Financial Services Compensation Scheme (or FSCS for short).

• And compared to other UK banks, we're 4x better at stopping card fraud, and 3x better at stopping identity theft.

MANAGE YOUR SPENDING

• Get notified the second you pay, set budgets for things like groceries and going out, and get warnings if you're spending too fast (if you want them). Plus, fee-free spending abroad, and we don't mark up the exchange rate.

GET ON TOP OF YOUR BILLS

• Pick a Pot to pay bills from, so you can't accidentally spend the rent. We'll tell you if they're higher for the upcoming month, and remind you if you're running low. When they're due, we pay them for you - easy.

SAVE FOR THINGS THAT MATTER

• Earn interest from a growing number of savings options. Automatically put money aside when you spend, round up payments to watch the pennies turn into pounds, and choose images to stay focused on your goals.

GETTING PAID WITH MONZO IS MAGIC

• If you're paid by Bacs (most people are!), then we can advance you your salary a day early, for free. Then effortlessly sort your salary between spending, bills and savings. All your money neatly separated so you can't overspend, but still under one roof. A heads up: we can stop offering get paid early, or change this service, at any time.

AND THERE'S MORE...

• Easy, instant bank transfers. Split bills with a tap, and send money with just a link, or over bluetooth to anyone nearby. And we're here with friendly human help, if you need us.

BUILDING WITH YOU

• We've built a new kind of bank, and we've built it together. We care about being open and doing what's right by our customers.

• Our community of customers are at the heart of everything we do: they chose our name, have suggested features and helped us decide what to build. We'd love you to join them.

DON'T JUST TAKE OUR WORD FOR IT

"Monzo? It might just be the future of banking." — The Guardian
"A bank for people who hate banks." — Bloomberg
"Monzo is a bank designed for the world we live in today." — TechCrunch


Monzo Bank Limited is a company registered in England and Wales (No. 09446231). Eligibility and T&Cs apply.
results.releaseNotes: Are you a business owner on the hunt for an account that just works, so you can too? From this week on, you can apply for a Monzo Business account without opening a personal account. Obviously we’d love you to get both, but don’t worry – we know it’s not personal, it’s strictly business.

Beep Saúde | A maior empresa de saú de domiciliar do Brasil

Baixe o app e viva a melhor experiência em saúde domiciliar. Vacinas e exames a poucos cliques da sua casa. 

Na Beep Saúde, tecnologia  e medicina se unem para que você cuide da sua saúde, e de quem você ama, com praticidade, segurança e conforto. ESQUEÇA A HISTÓRIA DE QUE EM CASA É MAIS CARO! Nossos serviços de exames e vacinação em casa têm valores competitivos, portanto, cuidar da sua saúde com a Beep também é saudável para a sua economia.

EXAMES 
Todos os nossos exames são processados pela Dasa, que é líder do setor de medicina diagnóstica no país, com marcas que são referência em saúde (Sérgio Franco, Bronstein, Lâmina e Alta, entre outras).

VACINAÇÃO fixas no Calendário Vacinal do Ministério da Saúde, quanto as recomendadas pela Sociedade Brasileira de Imunizações. Nossas vacinas são dos melhores fabricantes do mercado: GSK, MSD, Pfizer e Sanofi. Na Beep Saúde, você se vacina em casa com segurança!

VACINAÇÃO DOMICILIAR | VACINA EM CASA DE DOMINGO A DOMINGO
Esqueça a ideia que "em casa é mais caro". A tecnologia, aliada à nossa experiência, torna possível o serviço "Vacina em Casa" com valores mais do que competitivos.

ATENDIMENTO DE EXCELÊNCIA
O time de enfermagem da Beep Saúde é submetido a um rigoroso processo seletivo composto de teste técnico, avaliação comportamental e dinâmicas de grupo. Após a contratação, as profissionais passam por treinamento teórico - incluindo treinamento comportamental - e prático. Durante esse período, elas são avaliadas pela liderança e só assumem a posição e iniciam as atividades quando estão 100% preparadas para encantar no atendimento. Saúde em Casa é coisa séria!
